title: Ukrainian borscht with caraway dumplings
summary: The recipe Ukrainian borscht with caraway dumplings could satisfy your Eastern European craving in approximately 3 hours. This recipe makes 12 servings with 364 calories, 14g of protein, and 23g of fat each. For $1.51 per serving, this recipe covers 16% of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. A mixture of caraway seeds, olive oil, cabbage, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so tasty. To use up the flour you could follow this main course with the Apple Tart with Caramel Sauce as a dessert. 1 person has made this recipe and would make it again. With a spoonacular score of 77%, this dish is pretty good. Try Ukrainian Borscht, Ukrainian Borscht, and How To Make Ukrainian Borscht for similar recipes.
